{
  "stem": "17372.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 317.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He sent one German to Auschwitz, to Birkenau, where my wife was-- there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The same thing happened to women.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Instead of Brunnlitz, they sent them to Auschwitz, to Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they-- Helene was there-- a few weeks in there in terrible condition, shivering, no food, no drink water.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She was drinking water from gutters.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She got the typhoid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "She was very sick.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And one day, a German came and called by name these 300 women.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "That was unheard in history.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "By-- was saying that only way out of Auschwitz is through the chimney.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And he called the 300 women.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And my wife was in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And one day, they brought them to Brunnlitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My wife was in terrible condition.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "At other concentration camp, they would shoot her straight away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But instead, they put her in the hospital.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And she get back to her hurt slowly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And also I said to Oskar, Herr Schindler, they took our, our instruments, accordion and violin.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Don't worry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "He sent one German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And with next day, he came.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "On his back, he brought my accordion and my brother, the Guadagnini violin, which he had till now.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I opened accordion-- unscrewed the side.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "There was that 100 mark.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "You can't imagine what a fortune that was in there, especially my wife was so sick.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "I could buy on black markets some food, something extra.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I must save her life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Until today, I haven't got a clue.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It was sent from God.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was-- next to us, was a-- was a camp not so strict with Poles.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And through the wire, a tall-- in Brunnlitz wasn't such a-- so strict as other camps.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, this factory, he put a huge machines making a lot of noise.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
